					Full Description



		DKSH Holdings (Malaysia) Berhad (DKSH) is a Malaysia-based market expansion services provider. The Company operates through three segments, including Marketing and distribution services, Logistics services and Others. The Company's business segments focus on the fields of consumer goods, healthcare and performance materials, and offer a range of Market Expansion Services to business partners in their respective areas. It provides a portfolio of services ranging from marketing, to providing sales force, distribution and logistics, invoicing and credit control, handling of inventory and returned goods and other services. Its Logistics services segment focuses on supply chain services ranging from import to forwarding, warehousing and distribution, order processing and collections. This also includes the distribution of prepaid telephone cards. Others segment is engaged in the Famous Amos chocolate chip cookie business. It has over 90 Famous Amos outlets located in West and East Malaysia.
» Full Overview of DELM.KL







