Company Overview of DKSH Holdings (Malaysia) Berhad



Snapshot People




Company Overview
DKSH Holdings (Malaysia) Berhad, an investment holding company, provides market expansion services to consumer goods, healthcare, performance materials, and technology industries in Malaysia. The company operates through three segments: Marketing and Distribution Services, Logistics Services, and Others. It offers sourcing, market analysis and research, marketing and sales, distribution and logistics, and after-sales services, as well as invoicing and credit control, inventory and trade returns handling, and other value added services for consumer goods and performance materials. The company also provides supply chain services, including import, forwarding, warehousing and distribution, orde...
DKSH Holdings (Malaysia) Berhad, an investment holding company, provides market expansion services to consumer goods, healthcare, performance materials, and technology industries in Malaysia. The company operates through three segments: Marketing and Distribution Services, Logistics Services, and Others. It offers sourcing, market analysis and research, marketing and sales, distribution and logistics, and after-sales services, as well as invoicing and credit control, inventory and trade returns handling, and other value added services for consumer goods and performance materials. The company also provides supply chain services, including import, forwarding, warehousing and distribution, order processing, and sales collections for healthcare and consumer goods, as well as distributes prepaid telephone cards. In addition, it is involved in the retail of chocolate chip cookies, hampers, gifts, chocolates, and confectionery items, as well as in rental activities. The company was founded in 1923 and is headquartered in Petaling Jaya, Malaysia. DKSH Holdings (Malaysia) Berhad is a subsidiary of DKSH Resources (Malaysia) Sdn Bhd.
Detailed Description


