en  4.98   Prior Close  5.04 (08/01/17)     1 Day    DKSH -0.99%     DJIA 0.00%     Russell 2K -0.21%     Transportation/Logistics 0.34%                             Overview Profile     Overview Profile Financials Income Statement Balance Sheet Cash Flow Research & Ratings Historical Prices Options Advanced Charting              Company Info DKSH Holdings (Malaysia) Bhd        B-11-01, The Ascent, Paradigm Petaling Jaya Selangor 47301 Malaysia   Website Map       Employees  -    Sector  Transportation Services      Sales or Revenue  5.27 B    Industry  Transportation/Logistics      1Y Sales Change   -5.40%     Fiscal Year Ends  December 31 Download Reports                      Description DKSH Holdings (Malaysia) Bhd      DKSH Holdings (Malaysia) Bhd. is an investment company, which engages in the provision of market expansion services such as marketing; sales force; distribution and logistics; invoicing and credit control; handling of inventory and returned goods; and other value added services. It operates through the following segments: Marketing and Distribution, Logistics, and Others. The Marketing and Distribution segment comprises the fast moving consumer goods and performance materials business. The Logistics segment provides warehousing and distribution, order processing, and sales collections for the healthcare business and parts of consumer goods business such as sales of telephone cards. The Others segment focuses on the Famous Amos chocolate chip cookie and central overheads businesses including property. The company was founded on December 24, 1991 and is headquartered in Petaling Jaya, Malaysia.    expand             Key People DKSH Holdings (Malaysia) Bhd   Board of Directors    Name/Title Current Board Membership          Jason Michael Nicholas McLaren, 39  CFO, Executive Director & Group Finance Director   DKSH Holdings (Malaysia) Bhd.      Stephen John Ferraby, 52  Non-Independent Non-Executive Director   DKSH Holdings (Malaysia) Bhd.      Teng Ha